    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……描いても描いても終わりませんわ……\nfranさん、もう諦めた方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… No matter how much I draw‚ there’s no end in sight…\nFran-san‚ maybe we should give up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.3309750239
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.33333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "諦めないわよ！　ページ数も削る気ないから\nここで諦めたら、編集部になんて言えばいいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t give up! I’m not cutting down the page count either!\nWhat am I supposed to say to the editorial department if I give up now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3492065747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "バナナの皮で滑って転んで\n利き手の指を全部突き指したと素直に言うしか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just tell them you slipped on a banana peel and fell‚\nand sprained all the fingers on your dominant hand…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "あの事故自体が、ギャグ漫画みたいだったわよね……\nそのせいで、スケジュールが大幅に遅れちゃったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That accident itself was like something out of a gag manga…\nBecause of that‚ the schedule’s been pushed back so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5230390231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.3230390231
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "もう三日も缶詰中ですわよ……\n缶詰になるなら、せめてホテルが良かったですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve been cooped up here for three days straight…\nIf we’re going to be stuck working‚ I wish we were at least stuck in a hotel…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.3495246251
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "言い訳なんてしてもしょうがないわよ\nいい？　プロなんだから、やると言ったからにはやるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Making excuses won’t get us anywhere.\nYou got it? Professionals do what they say they’ll do!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9615657806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、すずと遙子も復唱しなさい\n私は天才、やれば出来る！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ Suzu and Haruko‚ repeat after me.\nI’m a genius‚ I can do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.95544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私は天才、やれば出来る……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m a genius‚ I can do it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9554438273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.4667383511
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "徹夜上等！　寝なきゃ余裕！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All-nighter! Bring it on! We just need to stay awake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4667383511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.3919315814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "て、徹夜上等……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-all-nighter…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3919315814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "寝なきゃ余裕……\nって、さすがにブラック過ぎますわ～～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We just need to stay awake…\nIsn’t this a bit too much exploitation!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3619207404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3619207404
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.6887529213
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.2999969483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "うるさいうるさいっ、私は一人でも描くから！\n燃えろペン！　見さらせっ、私の才能ーーーー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shut up‚ shut up! I’ll draw it myself!\nBurn‚ pen! Unleash my talent----!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2999969483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.17442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "深夜テンション過ぎますわよ～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t your energy level a bit too high for this time of night!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1744222163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.3748937446
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "んん……もう食べられませんわ～……\n……ハッ！　私としたことが、寝落ちするなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I can’t eat anymore…\n…Huh! To think that I‚ of all people‚ would fall asleep…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2999933879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.3331020194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "（遙子さんも寝てしまっていますわね……）\n（締め切り間近とはいえ、根を詰め過ぎですわ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Haruko-san is asleep too…）\n（Even though the deadline is approaching‚ we’re pushing ourselves too hard…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6333267212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.9354605196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子はなんでマスコットキャラなんて描いてるのよ……\n下書きにないでしょうが。魔法少女物みたいだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko‚ why are you drawing a mascot character?\nIt wasn’t in the rough draft. It looks like something out of a magical girl anime…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7666600545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.8206988492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "すずはすずで、勝手にキャラの髪型変えてるし……\nしかもこの髪型、すずにそっくりだし……直しとこっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Suzu is changing the character’s hairstyle without permission…\nAnd this hairstyle… It looks exactly like Suzu’s… I’ll fix it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0666600545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.6703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "え……franさん？\n本当に、一人で作業を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… fran-san?\nYou really did all the work… by yourself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4999933879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.112242174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "……？　あぁ、起きたならそこ、ベタ塗っといて\nまぁ私の漫画だし、最悪、私がなんとかするけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…? Oh‚ if you’re awake‚ ink that part over there.\nWell‚ it’s my manga. So I’ll figure it out if I have to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8999933879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.8615399518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "あ……いえ。手伝うと言ったのは私ですし\nプロとして、ちゃんと最後までやりますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… no. I’m the one who said I would help.\nSo as a professional‚ I’ll see it through to the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.0999933879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.6864383536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "その……franさんって、凄いですわね\nビッグマウスなところはありますけど、その分……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know… fran-san‚ you’re amazing.\nYou might be a bit of a big talker‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.2333267212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
