      "text": "「出来がいいから」って\n編集部の人が、漫画雑誌の方にも載せてくれたのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said‚ “It’s really good”‚ and\nthe editorial staff even put it in the manga magazine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.9666844684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 219.0284331159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
