      "text": "こんなに評価してもらえると気分いいわ。漫画好きって\nいうのも、親近感があるってファンに言ってもらえたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels good to be praised like this. The fans said\nthat my love for manga makes me more relatable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.9666844684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 226.7627863404
