      "text": "流行の漫画を紹介する番組にも、呼ばれることに\nなったんですわよね？　kanaさんと一緒ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You even got invited to a TV show that introduces\npopular manga‚ right? with kana-san‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.2333511351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
