      "text": "そうね、おまけが引っ付いてくるのは癪だけど\n本当に癪だけど、仕事が増えるのはいいことだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. It’s annoying that she’s tagging along‚\nbut it’s good to have more work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.1333511351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 243.3453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
