      "text": "それにしてもfranさん、今回は頑張っていたわよね\nお金が一番、仕事は効率良く、っていう印象だったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ fran-san‚ you really worked hard this time.\nI had the impression that money was all that mattered to you‚ and you only cared about efficiency‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.8786709942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 254.5453396954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
