      "text": "別に、間違ってはいないわよ。割のいい仕事がしたいし\n効率の悪い仕事なんて、出来ればしたくないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’m not wrong about that. I want to do well-paying jobs‚\nand if I can help it‚ I don’t want to do inefficient work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.4333531696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 263.1851404028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
