      "text": "っていうかそんなの、誰でもそうでしょ？\n自分を信じるのも、仕事で手を抜かないのも当たり前よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ that’s how everyone is‚ right?\nBelieving in yourself and giving your all to your work are givens.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.7333531696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
