      "text": "当たり前ではあるけれど……\nそこまで出来るのって、凄いわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is‚ but…\nTo be able to do it to that extent is amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 275.8505975561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
