      "text": "自分を信じて、真っ直ぐに突き進む\nそれがfranさんらしさなのかもしれませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Believing in yourself and pushing forward.\nMaybe that’s what makes you‚ you‚ fran-san.",
